  %p The interrogatives #{t "каде", "kadé"} “what kind of?”<sup>4</sup>, #{t "какове", "kákove"} “what kind of?” (in free variation with каде), and #{t "котре", "kótre"} “which?” decline as adjectives, because they directly modify a noun. They are all regular.
